what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Created CTEs for selective dimension filters (date_dim d1, item, customer_demographics, household_demographics) and pre-filtered catalog_sales, then joined these reduced datasets in the main query.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
